{{Vgname|三合會之戰|en=Triad Wars}}是一款由[[United_Front_Games|United Front Games]]和[[史克威尔艾尼克斯|史克威尔艾尼克斯倫敦工作室]]共同開發、[[史克威尔艾尼克斯|史克威尔艾尼克斯]]發行的[[開放世界|開放世界]][[動作冒險遊戲|動作冒險遊戲]]，為《[[香港秘密警察|香港秘密警察]]》之續作，惟已终止运营。

2013年10月7日，遊戲開發商United Front Games確認他們正在開發一款名為《三合會之戰》的遊戲，這款遊戲將會基于《熱血無賴》开发。開發商確定本作將由史克威尔艾尼克斯發行，2014年9月正式对外公佈。<ref name="SDsequel">{{cite web|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2013/10/07/sleeping-dogs-universe-sequel-triad-wars-in-development|title='Sleeping Dogs Universe' Sequel Triad Wars in Development|author=Mitch Dyer|publisher=IGN|date=2013-10-07|accessdate=07-10-2013|archive-date=2020-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200111120324/https://uk.ign.com/articles/2013/10/07/sleeping-dogs-universe-sequel-triad-wars-in-development}}</ref>United Front Games稱三合會之戰是“我們一直想做的一件作品。”<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.computerandvideogames.com/441814/sleeping-dogs-dev-teases-triad-wars-image/ Triad Wars Image Teaser|title= Sleeping Dogs dev teases Triad Wars image|author= Andy Robinson|publisher= [[Computer_and_Video_Games|Computer and Video Games]]|date= 2013-12-09|accessdate= 2014-03-15|archive-date= 2014-02-11|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140211070315/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/441814/sleeping-dogs-dev-teases-triad-wars-image/|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/477174/triad-wars-is-a-pc-online-game/|title=Triad Wars is a 'PC online game'|publisher=[[電腦與電子遊戲|CVG]]|author=Connor Sheridan|date=2014-09-19|accessdate=2014-09-19|archive-date=2014-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140920035050/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/477174/triad-wars-is-a-pc-online-game/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年1月开始运营，<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.unitedfrontgames.com/games/triad-wars/ |title= Triad Wars |author=  |website=  |publisher= United Front Games |language= en |accessdate= 2014-09-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140923142613/http://www.unitedfrontgames.com/games/triad-wars/ |archive-date= 2014-09-23 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>2016年1月20日，该游戏终止运营。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Futter|first1=Mike|title=Square Enix Shutting Down Free-To-Play Sleeping Dogs Success|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/a